# DataStar + Bun POC Project

This is a Proof of Concept (POC) project that demonstrates the minimal setup required to get Bun working with Data-star.

## Project Documentation

All relevant documentation for the LLM to reference is available in the `.cursor/docs/` directory. This includes:
- Bun runtime/toolkit documentation.
- Data-Star library documentation.

When working on this project, the AI should check the `.cursor/docs/` directory for any relevant documentation that might help with the current task.


## Project Philosophy

This project is laser-focused on **extreme simplicity** and **minimal code**. Key principles:
- Adding new dependencies is highly discouraged
- Solutions should use the minimum possible lines of code
- Keep everything as straightforward as possible
